{"type": "article", "id": 27379, "title": "鲸鱼数码钢琴", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-27T06:53:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132810U4DTRcwi9XZyhmzK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>你有没有幻想过未来的钢琴会是什么样？最近波兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.robertmajkut.com/\">Robert Majkut</a> 根据自己的一个梦设计了这款名为 Whaletone 的<a href=\"http://www.whaletone.com/products/royal-digital\">数码钢琴</a>，外型就好像是鲸鱼出水时那样有着流畅的曲线。优雅的造型和钢琴悠扬的声音结合，带给人全新的视听感受，也是对现有钢琴设计的一种挑战。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132807rsP9CKWYOfRdp6zo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132808Q7JrwcPtSd4Lj0va.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132809gCG5Inb6zeSYiM1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132809qZTR5aPYCDQ8GyLK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}